<inglise> Article 8 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 8 </eesti>
<inglise> Regulation (EEC) No 1865/90 is hereby repealed. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;rus (EM&Uuml;) nr 1865/90 tunnistatakse kehtetuks. </eesti>
<inglise> Its provisions shall however continue to apply to assistance granted for the programme period 1994-99 under Regulation (EEC) No 2052/88. </inglise>
